bdfdaae4f83fad5797ebbd","tid":30053,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泛民：<br />\n支持一國兩制 踢走689<br />\n補選記住投泛民一票<br />\n保住1/3關鍵性少數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n守住關鍵一席乜乜乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係要撐泛民，係要反政府，集會人數夠多，你要做乜唔係泛民可以阻到。</blockquote><br />\n其實今時今日可以仲做d咩？"},{"pid":"cf78f2a3cffaa8c46fc43b7d9523a58838e1a097","tid":30053,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泛民：<br />\n支持一國兩制 踢走689<br />\n補選記住投泛民一票<br />\n保住1/3關鍵性少數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n守住關鍵一席乜乜乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係要撐泛民，係要反政府，集會人數夠多，你要做乜唔係泛民可以阻到。</blockquote><br />\n其實今時今日可以仲做d咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多時候成功都係意外機遇黎，可以做o既就係唔好抱住&quot;做乜都冇用&quot;o既失敗主義。積極制造多啲機會，雨革當日爆發都係人數積聚夠多之後o既變化，本來都係學民和理非o既集會黎。<br />\n<br />\n所以去左先，人數夠多果陣民眾做乜唔到泛民話事的。"},{"pid":"4d180204713ae85260a98bf65daafc4a7bb95808","tid":30053,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>泛民：<br />\n支持一國兩制 踢走689<br />\n補選記住投泛民一票<br />\n保住1/3關鍵性少數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n守住關鍵一席乜乜乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n守住郑松泰关键一席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7c5e92517ae4184f41be516327948187f897dc","tid":30053,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:49:17.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf2f1b9c3f2f9ac3e0fb8c2a4823353e83c4026","tid":30053,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:02:54.000Z","msg":"趕走一個689<br />\n跟住又來另一個689<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(特首 三司12局係由中央任命<br />\n跟據基本法104條及釋法宣誓效忠)"},{"pid":"3a8238fd62b33bf2496156096fc75c9a5e995c13","tid":30053,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2